{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673020/extras/WordRelay_Title_small.png?t=1731272645\" /><br>READ, REMEMBER, and WRITE words in a sequence, adhering to a simple rule: the word must begin with the same letter that the previous word ended with. A competitive word battle. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673020/extras/Running.gif?t=1731272645\" /><br><br>Strategically build your list of words, strive for the longest ones, try getting bonus points, and remember opponents' words, which you can cleverly incorporate into future games. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673020/extras/bonusScroll.gif?t=1731272645\" /><br><br>Scores are determined by evaluating several factors, including the quantity of legitimate words played, the length of each word, and any unsuccessful attempts made during a player's turn. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673020/extras/GREAT.gif?t=1731272645\" /><br><br>Whether you prefer solo play for practicing English words or competing against friends, Word Relay offers an exciting gaming experience. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673020/extras/smallflowers.gif?t=1731272645\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Unique games with changing bonus rules<br></li><li> Weekly quest to build vocabulary<br></li><li> Customizable games to play how you want<br></li><li> Attack or defend with strategic wordplay<br></li><li> Opportunity to learn new words within each game</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673020/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731272645","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_